Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.10,0:02:57.24,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,320)}第一话 震惊！我与姊姊是驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.40,0:03:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 原来是纪美子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在发呆看什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.87,0:03:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 姊姊是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.38,0:03:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她是我憧憬的人 真想成为像她那样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.88,0:03:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该不可能吧 因为我没有才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.49,0:03:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 实际操作才一个月耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.49,0:03:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才不过是初学者 以后会越来越熟练的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本周处女座的运势如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.86,0:04:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运日是6号 会有很棒的邂逅等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.50,0:04:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你到底要怨叹到什么时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.37,0:04:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五六节的机械人操作课 听说是全校一起参与喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.91,0:04:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说新的教练也会来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快换衣服去练习吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.69,0:04:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,188 189 190 191 192 193 194
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.39,0:04:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,195 196 197 198 199 200
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跳绳明明很厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.80,0:04:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这个可以这么棒 对机械兵器却不行呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对机械真的很没辄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我同一时间 无法做两件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.88,0:04:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要看屏幕又要动手脚 这种事我放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.95,0:04:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 看来你很有自信嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.95,0:04:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在练习跳绳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要理她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经习惯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们不一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是提督的女儿 真叫人羡慕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想靠关系合格吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.00,0:05:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉喔 这是实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.27,0:05:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.24,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.54,0:05:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你们也想成为驾驶员 对自己要稍微放尊重一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.16,0:05:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是高屋法子吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.14,0:05:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.47,0:05:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你就是高屋提督的女儿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.21,0:05:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是同情你的遭遇 你一定很辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.45,0:05:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我已经习惯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.72,0:05:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械兵器的操纵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.79,0:06:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要同时注意6个平衡器 以及手脚的2个回传器就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次要做这么多事啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.20,0:06:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是怎么操作屏幕的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.97,0:06:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…一面看一面想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.87,0:06:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在下个瞬间 该做的事情 身体就会自动帮我做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 你真的是天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.05,0:06:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的 高屋 要达到这种地步是要努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.35,0:06:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 努力吗？ 那你就是努力的天才啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.86,0:06:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是在驾驶机械人的 第一天就跌倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.49,0:06:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从隔天起 我就开始练习如何不跌倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要肯努力 你也可以做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.83,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…怎么可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.27,0:06:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你的头发看来有点碍事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好好加油吧 高屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.69,0:07:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来她没救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.34,0:07:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.57,0:07:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本周处女座的运势如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.78,0:07:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运日是6号 会有很棒的邂逅等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.41,0:07:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶 今天是我人生中 最棒的一天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.79,0:07:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前看齐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.43,0:07:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.07,0:07:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从Luxion的悲剧发生至今 已经过了6年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了对付敌人的宇宙怪兽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.57,0:08:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界各地共同进行的 RX计划已开始了5年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.28,0:08:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 上次那个计划 听说隔壁男生部 派出的两名人选好像已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边一定是 派姊姊去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.65,0:08:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但问题是 另一个人要派谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.52,0:08:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说会从全校里选出 所以我们也有机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.53,0:08:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 若能跟憧憬的姊姊 一起上宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.76,0:08:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我死也甘心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.53,0:08:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 怎么可能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.50,0:08:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是三年级的柏原啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.14,0:08:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且听说这次来的教练是中校呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.97,0:08:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像是为了这个计划 特地来这里赴任的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.68,0:08:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 是教练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.45,0:08:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是从今天开始要指导你们 操作机械兵器的太田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.72,0:08:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法跟上的人 我会毫不留情的当掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.79,0:08:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 我要把大家的 自动平衡器关掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.29,0:08:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后不许再用它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手动操作是实战必要的基本能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.51,0:09:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法自己站好的家伙 给我从学科开始重念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来去跑操场50圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.55,0:09:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喊出声音！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.45,0:09:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.89,0:09:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？奇怪？我想想… 跑步…跑步是…这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的一年级菜鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.65,0:09:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我从机械兵器上滚下来 用自己的脚跑操场50圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经是放学时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.53,0:10:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还待在校园里的学生 请赶快回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.17,0:10:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法子 法子快点回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在这里睡觉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.21,0:10:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 我动不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.85,0:10:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你死要面子 真的跑完了50圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.29,0:10:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 来吧 快点换衣服 回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.81,0:10:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.58,0:10:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.72,0:10:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（代表选出）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.99,0:11:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（天野和美、高屋法子）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（高屋法子）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.36,0:11:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她爸爸是那个 遭到全数歼灭的舰队提督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.13,0:11:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她是靠关系 而当上驾驶员的啰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.00,0:11:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问吗？ 她动作真的很迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天不是也看到了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.57,0:11:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教练真是偏心 真讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.61,0:11:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天只会奉承
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.61,0:11:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸都被全灭了 竟然还想靠这种方法接近姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.71,0:11:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然得跟那个全灭女搭档 姊姊真可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.66,0:11:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对于教练在想什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.50,0:11:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对于教练在想什么 实在搞不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.50,0:11:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子驾驶机械兵器 还不到一个月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.91,0:11:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上宇宙的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.04,0:11:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得同样是三年级的 柏原会比较适合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.05,0:12:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说那孩子是 高屋提督的独生女是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.86,0:12:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是提督所指挥的宇宙战舰 Luxion的幸存者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.60,0:12:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才找她去当驾驶员…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.03,0:12:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.40,0:12:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 这个计划 比你想象中的更重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.37,0:12:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是赌上人类存亡的难题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为何…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.21,0:12:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责人就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.95,0:12:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是她 或许办得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.38,0:12:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.08,0:12:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buster机组 上了宇宙你就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.75,0:12:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教练是爸爸船上的幸存者？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.54,0:12:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办？法子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.24,0:13:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不但被姊姊彻底的讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.21,0:13:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又因为爸爸的关系 当上驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被全校当成全民公敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.72,0:13:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？ 真是倒霉到家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本周处女座的运势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.69,0:13:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心被周围的人误解和麻烦事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.80,0:13:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 既然都已经被选上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.06,0:13:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能好好努力 让它能动不就好了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.13,0:13:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.03,0:13:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家不要这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.97,0:14:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.62,0:14:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你 请不要再欺负我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.39,0:14:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说我选上你的那件事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会觉得我在欺负你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.16,0:14:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我根本没有那个能力 绝对没有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一点希望也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.66,0:14:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在说你对我偏心 而且还要我跟天野学姊搭档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.64,0:14:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过份了 太残忍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说的只有这些吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.15,0:14:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要成为驾驶员的你 所欠缺的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.02,0:14:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野她有是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.97,0:15:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.84,0:15:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你缺乏的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊她穿着铁木屐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.05,0:15:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野她的确有天分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.38,0:15:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 比那个更重要 塑造出她的能力的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.42,0:15:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她自己的努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.65,0:15:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 要达到这种地步是要努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.59,0:15:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的确没有才能 因为你根本就缺乏努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.40,0:15:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你有天分 所以才会选上你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.44,0:15:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高屋 努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.97,0:15:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨练自己的能力 不要依靠别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.11,0:15:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 自己用全身去感受 用头脑去想 用心去判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙中可以依靠的 只有自己而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.71,0:15:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.62,0:15:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 与天野一起上宇宙吧 有些事你必须要去完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.27,0:17:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以为她马上就会辞退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.24,0:17:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到她还蛮努力的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表现得不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本动作变得熟练多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.75,0:17:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的 因为教练一直陪着她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会变得更加熟练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.61,0:18:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教练 我哪里比不上高屋？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.71,0:18:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.62,0:18:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没必要回答你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.82,0:18:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一副丢人样 柏原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.90,0:18:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你升上少尉 高屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天终于要出发了 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.87,0:18:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 今天放学后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不可以给我点时间？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.81,0:18:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.75,0:18:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶你自己的机械兵器来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.43,0:18:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你会在出发前就放弃 没想到你蛮努力的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.60,0:18:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你自己不放弃的话 就由我来帮你放弃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要上了 全灭女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.94,0:19:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离9.7 8.5 那个…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是跑步就已经费尽全力的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.96,0:19:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来根本无法兼顾格斗战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.74,0:19:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.64,0:19:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.95,0:19:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法子 你不要紧吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.67,0:20:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教练 不要再让她们打了 再打下去就不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法子她太可怜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.21,0:20:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么？ 实战可不只是这样而已喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.71,0:20:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.78,0:20:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算其它人认同你 我可绝对不认同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.22,0:20:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教练 教练 我该怎么办？教练…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.86,0:20:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要依靠别人 用全身去感受 用心去判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.93,0:20:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 是我不够集中 总是特别在意监视器的画面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监视器关掉了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.28,0:20:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她竟然做这种事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.85,0:20:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟…竟然没把我放在眼里 你这下完了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.23,0:21:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三角锥拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.77,0:21:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞…飞起来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.81,0:21:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪电踢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.93,0:21:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.67,0:21:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶机械兵器才一个月的女孩 竟能使出闪电踢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.54,0:21:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人难以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.52,0:22:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高屋 天野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.72,0:22:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们迟早会成为前锋游击 机械兵器部队的TOP部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.83,0:22:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真正的困难从现在才要开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.10,0:22:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了成为真正的TOP部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.34,0:22:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了成为真正能够守护人群 拯救朋友的宇宙战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.25,0:22:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃努力 要克服它 然后战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.26,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的富士山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.23,0:23:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标成为TOP部队是吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.81,0:24:01.27,SongChn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}像妹妹一样的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.81,0:24:01.27,SongJap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いもうと みたい そんざい だって
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.28,0:24:06.11,SongChn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你小声地回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.28,0:24:06.11,SongJap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あなた が こたえ つぶやいた の よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.11,0:24:10.82,SongChn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}抱着必死决心的告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.11,0:24:10.82,SongJap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ひっし だった こくはく
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.82,0:24:14.82,SongChn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就在周日随风而散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.82,0:24:14.82,SongJap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}かぜ に ちった にちようび
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.82,0:24:19.39,SongChn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在太阳底下被拒绝时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.82,0:24:19.39,SongJap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}たいよう の した ふられちゃう とね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.39,0:24:24.17,SongChn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}根本就轮不到泪水上场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.39,0:24:24.17,SongJap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}なみだ なんか も でばん が なくて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.17,0:24:31.57,SongChn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只能茫然的朝着你的背影挥手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.17,0:24:31.57,SongJap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ただ ボーゼン と せなか に て を ふった の…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.57,0:24:33.58,SongChn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}真是没出息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.57,0:24:33.58,SongJap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}なさけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.58,0:24:42.12,SongChn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}从那之后生活变得昏暗无光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.58,0:24:42.12,SongJap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}それ から もう くらやみ の ひび
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.12,0:24:46.59,SongChn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不过Encore恋爱的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.12,0:24:46.59,SongJap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}でも ね アンコール こい する パワー
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.59,0:24:51.03,SongChn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在内心Encore纯真的冲劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.59,0:24:51.03,SongJap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}むね に アンコール むじゃき な ファイト
